## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b8b5-106">Das folgende Beispiel ist Teil einer benutzerdefinierten Sprachsynthese Implementierung, die <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>von, und verwendet wird.<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b8b5-106">The following example is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b8b5-107">Die Implementierung von<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b8b5-107">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
